thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text: Puzzles arrived in very good time. The quality was very very good. And they were really a lot of fun to put together because of a lot of variation in the colors. I was amazed at the brightness of the colors! A little pricey, but would definitely consider buying more.
